PN,31701
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1775769064
OL,3,CRising mortgage costs dent buyer
OL,4,Cdemand amid 'housing market mood shift'
OL,6,FRising mortgage costs have dented
OL,7,Fdemand from buyers in the property
OL,8,Fmarket, dampening longer-term
OL,9,Fexpectations for house prices,
OL,10,Faccording to surveyors.
OL,12,FThe Royal Institution of Chartered
OL,13,FSurveyors (Rics) said the housing
OL,14,Fmarket was losing momentum in March as
OL,15,Frising borrowing costs and wider
OL,16,Fgeopolitical uncertainty weighed
OL,17,Fheavily on buyer confidence and sales
OL,18,Factivity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1775769064
OL,3,CRising mortgage costs dent buyer
OL,4,Cdemand amid 'housing market mood shift'
OL,6,FA net balance of 39% of professionals
OL,7,Fsaw new buyer inquiries falling rather
OL,8,Fthan rising, deteriorating from a
OL,9,Fbalance of 29% who saw this in
OL,10,FFebruary.
OL,12,FThis was the weakest reading since
OL,13,FAugust 2023, as housing market
OL,14,Foptimism seen earlier in the year
OL,15,Ffaded.
OL,17,FAgreed sales also deteriorated, with a
OL,18,Fnet balance of 34% of professionals
OL,19,Fseeing falls, down from a balance of
OL,20,F13% who saw this the previous month.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1775769064
OL,3,CRising mortgage costs dent buyer
OL,4,Cdemand amid 'housing market mood shift'
OL,6,FRics said the report points to a
OL,7,Fmarket increasingly pressured by
OL,8,Finflationary concerns and higher
OL,9,Fmortgage costs.
OL,11,FA net balance of 33% of professionals
OL,12,Fexpect sales activity to weaken
OL,13,Ffurther over the next few months.
OL,15,FLooking 12 months ahead, a net balance
OL,16,Fof just 1% of professionals expect
OL,17,Fsales to weaken, indicating a broadly
OL,18,Fflat market.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1775769064
OL,3,CRising mortgage costs dent buyer
OL,4,Cdemand amid 'housing market mood shift'
OL,6,FA balance of 23% of professionals saw
OL,7,Fhouse prices falling rather than
OL,8,Frising in March.
OL,10,FPrice expectations for the next three
OL,11,Fmonths also weakened, with a net
OL,12,Fbalance of 43% of professionals
OL,13,Fexpecting falls. Looking a year ahead,
OL,14,Fa balance of 2% of professionals
OL,15,Fexpect price increases, pointing to
OL,16,Flittle overall price growth over the
OL,17,Fyear ahead.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1775769064
OL,3,CRising mortgage costs dent buyer
OL,4,Cdemand amid 'housing market mood shift'
OL,6,FLooking across the UK, London, East
OL,7,FAnglia, the South East and the South
OL,8,FWest all posted weaker price readings
OL,9,Fthan the national average, while
OL,10,FScotland and Northern Ireland
OL,11,Fcontinued to report rising prices.
OL,13,FOn the supply side, new instructions
OL,14,Fto sell remained subdued and the
OL,15,Famount of unsold stock on estate
OL,16,Fagents' books rose to an average of 47
OL,17,Fproperties, up from around 45 at the
OL,18,Fstart of the year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1775769064
OL,3,CRising mortgage costs dent buyer
OL,4,Cdemand amid 'housing market mood shift'
OL,6,FIn the lettings market, a mismatch
OL,7,Fbetween demand and supply continued,
OL,8,Fwith demand for homes from tenants
OL,9,Frising while landlord instructions
OL,10,Fcontinued to decrease, Rics said.
OL,12,FTarrant Parsons, Rics head of market
OL,13,Fresearch and analysis, said: "The mood
OL,14,Facross the UK housing market has
OL,15,Fshifted markedly over the past couple
OL,16,Fof months.
OL,26,@uD@^OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1775769064
OL,3,CRising mortgage costs dent buyer
OL,4,Cdemand amid 'housing market mood shift'
OL,6,F"What had been a cautiously improving
OL,7,Fpicture for activity has been knocked
OL,8,Foff course by the wider macro fallout
OL,9,Ffrom the Middle East conflict, as the
OL,10,Frenewed deterioration in the mortgage
OL,11,Frate outlook has proved particularly
OL,12,Fchallenging.
OL,14,F"Indeed, with average fixed rates
OL,15,Fclimbing back above 5% according to
OL,16,Fsome sources, it is unsurprising that
OL,17,Fbuyer demand has softened.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1775769064
OL,3,CRising mortgage costs dent buyer
OL,4,Cdemand amid 'housing market mood shift'
OL,6,F"The path ahead hinges on whether or
OL,7,Fnot recent surges in oil and energy
OL,8,Fcosts begin to reverse in what remains
OL,9,Fa highly uncertain geopolitical
OL,10,Fenvironment."
OL,12,FOn Wednesday, financial information
OL,13,Fwebsite Moneyfacts said mortgage rates
OL,14,Fare likely to remain higher for "some
OL,15,Ftime yet" despite some signs of the
OL,16,Fupward pressure easing.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@MO]vD@aOUwD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1775769064
OL,3,CRising mortgage costs dent buyer
OL,4,Cdemand amid 'housing market mood shift'
OL,6,FGlobal stock markets have been
OL,7,Frecovering after the US and Iran
OL,8,Fagreed a two-week ceasefire, and
OL,9,FMoneyfacts said that calming markets
OL,10,Fshould have a stabilising impact on
OL,11,Fthe mortgage market.
OL,13,FAdam French, head of consumer finance
OL,14,Fat Moneyfacts, said: "The longer the
OL,15,Fceasefire holds and markets calm, the
OL,16,Fmore the mortgage market will
OL,17,Fstabilise, and rates could even begin
OL,18,Fto edge lower.
OL,26,@vD@VOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1775769064
OL,3,CRising mortgage costs dent buyer
OL,4,Cdemand amid 'housing market mood shift'
OL,6,F"But for now, it's more likely to slow
OL,7,For pause increases rather than trigger
OL,8,Fany sharp falls."
OL,10,FJinesh Vohra, chief executive of
OL,11,Fmortgage app Sprive, said: "Strategies
OL,12,Flike regular overpayments or reducing
OL,13,Fyour balance earlier can have an
OL,14,Foutsized impact ` potentially saving
OL,15,Fhomeowners thousands over the term of
OL,16,Ftheir mortgage.
OL,18,F"In today's environment, it's not just
OL,19,Fabout getting on the ladder, but
OL,20,Fmanaging the cost of staying on it."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@QO]sD@\OUzD@AOU|D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
